    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi @AntoineDuComptoirDesPharmacies,\r\n\r\nThe values passed in `on` do need to be escaped for them to work properly with other widgets such as `CurrentRefinements`.\r\n\r\nOne way to apply negative filters would be to use `Configure` with `NOT brand:Apple` in `filters`.\r\n\r\nAlternatively you could create your own connector and use the [`toggleFacetExclusion`](https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/reference.html#AlgoliaSearchHelper%23toggleFacetExclusion) method from the helper.",
